    "innerText": "Tato paṭṭhāya yāva ajjadivasā tasmiṃ ṭhāne naḷā ekacchiddāva honti. Imasmiñhi kappe kappaṭṭhiyapāṭihāriyāni nāma cande sasalakkhaṇaṃ (jā. 1.4.61 ādayo), vaṭṭajātake (jā. 1.1.35) saccakiriyaṭṭhāne aggijālassa āgamanupacchedo, ghaṭīkārassa mātāpitūnaṃ vasanaṭṭhāne anovassanaṃ (ma. ni. 2.291), pokkharaṇiyā tīre naḷānaṃ ekacchiddabhāvoti. Iti sā pokkharaṇī naḷena pānīyassa pivitattā ‘‘naḷakapānakā’’ti nāmaṃ labhi. Aparabhāge taṃ pokkharaṇiṃ nissāya nigamo patiṭṭhāsi, tassapi ‘‘naḷakapāna’’ntveva nāmaṃ jātaṃ. Taṃ pana sandhāya vuttaṃ ‘‘naḷakapāne’’ti. Palāsavaneti kiṃsukavane."
